<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-31-0402 </DOCNO><TEXT>New requirements in thorax-radiography like economy and low patient-dose,are of increasing importance. Using new concepts, these requirementstogether with high image-quality were fulfilled in a new thorax-system,the pulmo DIAGNOST 100. This was possible by the utilization of the slit-radiographyprinciple together with a linear image intensifier. It resulted in superiorquality for the fully automated system.</TEXT></DOC>